## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3863e-107">사용자 보안 주체 계정은 만들어질 때 유지 되지 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3863e-107">The user principal account is not persisted when it is created.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3863e-108">계정에 저장 하려면 호출을 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A> 메서드.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3863e-108">To save the account, call the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3863e-109">다음 코드 예제에서는 사용자 이름이 LDAP 도메인 "fabrikam.com"에 연결 하 고 암호 초기화는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> "관리자" 및 "securelyStoredPassword." 생성자</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3863e-109">The following code example connects to the LDAP domain "fabrikam.com" with the username and password initialized in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor to "administrator" and "securelyStoredPassword."</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3863e-110">사용자 이름 및 전자 메일 주소와 같은 예제에서는 설정 된 속성에 지정 된 컨테이너에서 생성 됩니다는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> 생성자: "CN = Users, DC = fabrikam, DC = com입니다."</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3863e-110">The properties set in the example, such as user name and email address, are created under the container specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor: "CN=Users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com."</span></span>  
  
```  
  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(  
                                         ContextType.Domain,  
                                         "fabrikam.com",   
                                         "CN=Users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com",  
                                         "administrator",   
                                         "securelyStoredPassword");   
  
UserPrincipal usr = new UserPrincipal(ctx);  
  
usr.Name = "Jim Daly";  
usr.Description = "This is the user account for Jim Daly";  
usr.EmailAddress = "jimdaly@fabrikam.com";  
usr.SetPassword("securelyStoredPassword");  
usr.Save();  
  
usr.Dispose();  
ctx.Dispose();   
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3863e-167">다음 코드는 로컬 컴퓨터 저장소에 연결합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3863e-167">The following code connects to the local computer store.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3863e-168">자격 증명에 지정 되지 않은 있으므로 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> 생성자, 현재 스레드가 되는 실행 중인 사용자의 자격 증명입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3863e-168">Since the credentials are not specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor, the credentials of the user running the current thread are used.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3863e-169">SamAccountName "게스트" 권한이 있는 사용자를 찾으려면 검색 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3863e-169">A search is performed to find the user who has SamAccountName "Guest".</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3863e-170">사용자를 찾을 경우이 사용자의이 계정이 사용 되는지 여부를 결정 하는 검사가 수행 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3863e-170">If the user is found, a check is performed to determine whether this user's account is enabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3863e-171">계정을 사용 하지 않는 경우 예제 코드를 사용 하도록 설정 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3863e-171">If the account is not enabled, the example code enables it.</span></span>  
  
```  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(ContextType.Machine);  
  
UserPrincipal usr = UserPrincipal.FindByIdentity(ctx,   
                                           IdentityType.SamAccountName,   
                                           "Guest");  
  
if(usr != null)  
{  
    if (usr.Enabled == false)  
        usr.Enabled = true;  
  
    usr.Save();  
    usr.Dispose();  
}  
ctx.Dispose();   
```
